Lambda Expression
-----------------

	is an anonymous function
	do not have any name or return type or modifiers.
	
steps to create lambda expression
	1. remove modifier
	2. remove name
	3. remove return type
	4. place arrow
	
	if the body has only one statement we don't have to put the curly braces.
	we don't need to explicitly declare the datatypes of the arguments.
	remove return statements in the body of the function.
	